dct_description_sm: Surveyor General's Office, Adelaide ; A. Vaughan, Photo-lithographer : (65) March 1891.
Shows lot numbers, drainage, railways, roads, various locations and facilities (reservoirs, quarries, schools, tunnels, stations, etc.), telegraph lines.
Dates signalling exchanges, openings, closures, confirmations (referring to canals, water sourcing?) throughout map.
Surveyor General's Office seal, "Price One Shilling."
